## New WNP CMS footer - cms/includes/wnp-footer.html

# Variables:
# $mozilla_link_attrs (attrs) - link to https://www.mozilla.org/
# $mozilla_foundation_link_attrs (attrs) - link to https://foundation.mozilla.org/
footer-visit-mozilla = ເຂົ້າເບິ່ງ <a { $mozilla_link_attrs }>{ -brand-name-mozilla-corporation }</a> ເຊິ່ງເປັນມູນນິທິທີ່ບໍ່ຫວັງຜົນກຳໄລ <a { $mozilla_foundation_link_attrs }> ຂອງ { -brand-name-mozilla-foundation }</a>.
# Variables:
# $years (string) - license years ©1998–2025
footer-contributors = ສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງເນື້ອຫານີ້ແມ່ນ { $years } ໂດຍຜູ້ປະກອບສ່ວນແຕ່ລະຄົນຈາກ mozilla.org.
# Variables:
# $license_attrs (attrs) - link to https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/foundation/licensing/website-content/
footer-license = ເນື້ອຫາຖືກເຜີຍແຜ່ພາຍໃຕ້ໃບອະນຸຍາດ <a { $license_attrs }>{ -brand-name-creative-commons }</a>.
footer-firefox-support = ການສະໜັບສະໜູນ { -brand-name-firefox }
footer-privacy-notice = ແຈ້ງການຄວາມເປັນສ່ວນຕົວ
footer-donate = ບໍລິຈາກໃຫ້ { -brand-name-mozilla }
footer-donate-v2 = ບໍລິຈາກໃຫ້ { -brand-name-mozilla-foundation }
footer-make-good-things = ສ້າງສິ່ງດີໆຮ່ວມກັນ
